<plot>John is a very intelligent eight year old with typical bus stop bullies and an interest in astrology. His perception of reality is shattered when he learns the news of his idol, his older brother Josh, has attempted suicide and is now mentally impaired. John must come to terms with this tragedy and struggle with the question of "what happened to his brother?"</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?651666</url></doc>
